":"G2543","lemma":"καίτοι","translit":"kaítoi","derivation":"from G2532 (καί) and G5104 (τοί);","strongs_def":"and yet, i.e. nevertheless","kjv_def":"although","pos":"particle","usage":"although(1x)"},"G2592":{"id":"G2592","lemma":"καρποφορέω","translit":"karpophoréō","derivation":"from G2593 (καρποφόρος);","strongs_def":"to be fertile (literally or figuratively)","kjv_def":"be (bear, bring forth) fruit(-ful)","pos":"verb"},"G2557":{"id":"G2557","lemma":"κακοῦργος","translit":"kakoûrgos","derivation":"from G2556 (κακός) and the base of G2041 (ἔργον);","strongs_def":"a wrong-doer, i.e. criminal","kjv_def":"evil-doer, malefactor","pos":"adjective","usage":"malefactor(3x)"},"G2514":{"id":"G2514","lemma":"καθαρότης","translit":"katharótēs","derivation":"from G2513 (καθαρός);","strongs_def":"cleanness (ceremonially)","kjv_def":"purification","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"purifying(1x)"},"G2566":{"id":"G2566","lemma":"καλλίον","translit":"kallíon","derivation":"neuter of the (irregular) comparative of G2570 (καλός);","strongs_def":"(adverbially) better than many","kjv_def":"very well","pos":"comparative"},"G2537":{"id":"G2537","lemma":"καινός","translit":"kainós","derivation":"of uncertain affinity; new (especially in freshness; while G3501 (νέος) is properly so with respect to age","kjv_def":"new","pos":"adjective","usage":"new(44x)"},"G2529":{"id":"G2529","lemma":"καθοράω","translit":"kathoráō","derivation":"from G2596 (κατά) and G3708 (ὁράω);","strongs_def":"to behold fully, i.e. (figuratively) distinctly apprehend","kjv_def":"clearly see","pos":"verb"},"G2539":{"id":"G2539","lemma":"καίπερ","translit":"kaíper","derivation":"from G2532 (καί) and G4007 (περ);","strongs_def":"and indeed, i.e. nevertheless or notwithstanding","kjv_def":"and yet, although","pos":"conjunction","usage":"though(5x)"},"G2530":{"id":"G2530","lemma":"καθότι","translit":"kathóti","derivation":"from G2596 (κατά);","strongs_def":"and G3739 (ὅς) and G5100 (τὶς); according to which certain thing, i.